<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>KHIKA CAWRAWL KUANG CHUNGAH CH88</title>
<key>F</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Khika lamhla cawrawl einak kuang chungah, Van Bawi ngakchuan sem kha
 puan zual in an thlim, Vancung arfi nih a ihnak ah an zoh, Bawi hniang
 Jesuh ramro cungah aa hngilh ko.

[V2]
 Cawrual an hram thawngin ngakchia sem aa hlau, Sihmanhsehlaw Bawi
 hniang Jesuh a tap lo, Kan dawt Bawipa Jesuh, van in run kan zoh, Fingrei
 cah tiang ka ihnak pawngah um tuah.

[V3]
 &quot;Ka kiangah um, Bawipa Jesuh,&quot; tiah kan nawl, Zungzal in ka pawngah um
 law, ka daw fawn, Ngakchia vialte thluachuah vanluh kan pe tuah, Van ah
 nang he um ti awkah ka tlakter.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>88</hymn_number>
</song>